WEBVTT

00:00.800 --> 00:03.002
What you talking 'bout,
Mr. D.?

00:03.004 --> 00:06.105
ADULT ADAM:
<i>Back in the '80s,</i>
<i>these were the dads on TV.</i>

00:06.107 --> 00:10.109
<i>They were loving, nurturing,</i>
<i>and, quite often,</i>
<i>millionaires.</i>

00:10.111 --> 00:11.010
(RECORD NEEDLE SCRATCHES)

00:11.012 --> 00:13.612
<i>Unfortunately,</i>
<i>none of these</i>
<i>were my father.</i>

00:13.614 --> 00:15.914
<i>Now this was my dad,</i>
<i>Murray Goldberg,</i>

00:15.916 --> 00:18.250
<i>a man who lacked</i>
<i>both patience and pants.</i>

00:18.252 --> 00:20.185
Why you gotta be a moron
all the time?

00:20.187 --> 00:21.487
(MOUTH FULL)
What did I do?

00:21.489 --> 00:22.321
How many times
I gotta tell ya?

00:22.323 --> 00:25.024
Don't touch
the damn thermostat!

00:25.026 --> 00:26.125
It's like 900 degrees
in here!

00:26.127 --> 00:29.428
You don't get that 'cause
you're in your underpants
all the time.

00:29.430 --> 00:31.997
The AC is
for emergency use only.

00:31.999 --> 00:34.266
What do you think
I'm made of, cold air?

00:34.268 --> 00:35.134
More like hot air.

00:35.136 --> 00:36.568
Oh, that's so damn funny.

00:36.570 --> 00:37.936
<i>That's how</i>
<i>I remember my dad...</i>

00:37.938 --> 00:40.939
<i>Pants-less, pissed off,</i>
<i>and far from a millionaire.</i>

00:40.941 --> 00:42.608
Don't touch
the damn thermostat!

00:42.610 --> 00:43.709
I mean, really?
How many times?

00:43.711 --> 00:46.745
<i>And then there was my mom,</i>
<i>Beverly Goldberg.</i>

00:46.747 --> 00:48.080
<i>She was always there</i>
<i>for us,</i>

00:48.082 --> 00:51.984
<i>even when she probably</i>
<i>shouldn't have been.</i>

00:51.986 --> 00:52.518
(GASPS)

00:52.520 --> 00:56.055
Ah! Ooh! Mom,
you gotta stop
watching me sleep.

00:56.057 --> 00:58.190
Well, if you'd let me stare
at you during the daytime,

00:58.192 --> 00:59.725
we wouldn't have to do
this little dance.

00:59.727 --> 01:01.360
I thought
I locked the door.

01:01.362 --> 01:02.227
(LAUGHS)
Oh, please.

01:02.229 --> 01:05.531
Get up.
(SINGSONGY) We're going
clothes shopping today!

01:05.533 --> 01:06.098
(CLICKS TONGUE)

01:06.100 --> 01:08.000
About that...
I... I was thinkin',

01:08.002 --> 01:12.171
can I pick out my own outfit
for the first day of school?

01:15.275 --> 01:18.177
Okay. What size pants
do you wear?

01:18.344 --> 01:19.411
Uh...

01:19.413 --> 01:21.947
Three... Large?

01:21.949 --> 01:23.782
(LAUGHS) See?
You need me.

01:23.784 --> 01:27.352
Mom, it's the first day
of seventh grade.
I wanna look cool.

01:27.354 --> 01:29.888
Well, who is cooler
than your mom?

01:29.890 --> 01:32.458
All...the people?

01:32.460 --> 01:33.792
(LAUGHS)

01:33.794 --> 01:35.394
You have
terrible morning breath.

01:35.396 --> 01:39.031
Brush your teeth,
get dressed, let's jam.

01:39.033 --> 01:40.499
(CURTAIN RINGS SWOOSH)
Mom!

01:40.501 --> 01:43.135
<i>And so I went back-to-school</i>
<i>shopping with my mom.</i>

01:43.137 --> 01:47.539
<i>I got new clothes</i>
<i>and new nightmares</i>
<i>all in one day.</i>

01:47.541 --> 01:48.407
Miss?
Whoa.

01:48.409 --> 01:52.177
I need the next size up
in these pants
for my little boy.

01:52.179 --> 01:54.046
These are too tight
in the crotchular region.

01:54.048 --> 01:57.316
<i>She wasn't want you'd call</i>
<i>great with boundaries.</i>

01:57.318 --> 01:58.350
In the crotchal region!

01:58.352 --> 02:02.187
I can't send my son
to school like this,
but I like the pants.

02:02.189 --> 02:04.790
<i>While my mom had</i>
<i>a hands-on approach,</i>

02:04.792 --> 02:06.291
<i>my dad, not so much.</i>

02:06.293 --> 02:08.527
Don't come in here.
I'm watching TV.

02:08.529 --> 02:11.029
Come on. I'm going out.
Give me 20 bucks.

02:11.031 --> 02:12.865
No.
I need it.

02:12.867 --> 02:13.565
No.

02:13.567 --> 02:14.833
It's for my rap group.
No!

02:14.835 --> 02:17.035
How do you expect
Big Tasty to make it

02:17.037 --> 02:19.538
if his crew
can't cut a demo?

02:19.706 --> 02:21.940
Big Tasty?
(CHUCKLES)

02:21.942 --> 02:22.941
Who is Big Tasty?

02:22.943 --> 02:24.843
It's me!
It's my rap name.

02:24.845 --> 02:26.945
Your rap name should be
"Big Pain in my Ass."

02:26.947 --> 02:29.715
Now get out of here.
Go play in the street.

02:29.717 --> 02:30.883
Hey, Dad?
What?

02:30.885 --> 02:32.851
Can I have
20 bucks?
No.

02:32.853 --> 02:34.753
Please?
No!

02:34.888 --> 02:36.889
It's for girl stuff.

02:37.657 --> 02:38.190
Buh.

02:38.192 --> 02:41.360
<i>Lately, that's all</i>
<i>my dad could say</i>
<i>when it came to my sister.</i>

02:41.362 --> 02:43.929
Hey, Mom.
I need a Midol.

02:43.931 --> 02:45.397
Cramps.

02:45.765 --> 02:47.799
Buh. Ugh.

02:49.369 --> 02:50.702
Buh.

02:51.738 --> 02:53.205
(GASPS) Ugh.

02:55.475 --> 02:57.276
(WHISPERS) Girl stuff.

02:57.278 --> 03:00.946
You give Erica 20 bucks just
'cause she says "girl stuff"?

03:00.948 --> 03:02.948
My guy stuff has to
be worth something.

03:02.950 --> 03:05.751
It's not.
This isn't fair!

03:05.753 --> 03:07.719
God, I wish I was a girl!

03:07.721 --> 03:08.720
Got it.
No.

03:08.722 --> 03:11.790
No, that was
out of context.
Erase it. Erase it!

03:11.792 --> 03:14.927
Erase! Erase!
Erase that! Erase...

03:14.929 --> 03:15.561
Shame on you.

03:15.563 --> 03:19.031
I just sat down.
How'd we get shame
on me already?

03:19.033 --> 03:19.531
Barry's right.

03:19.533 --> 03:21.600
Ever since Erica grew
(WHISPERS) boobs...

03:21.602 --> 03:23.602
