You haven't known
how to deal with her.

03:23.604 --> 03:26.138
I mean, you don't even
yell at her anymore!

03:26.140 --> 03:28.740
Stop it. I yell at her
all the time.

03:28.742 --> 03:29.408
Oh, really?

03:29.410 --> 03:31.476
When was the last time
you called her a moron?

03:31.478 --> 03:34.780
She knows
I think she's a moron.
I don't have to say it.

03:34.782 --> 03:35.480
Yes, you do.

03:35.482 --> 03:37.249
She doesn't know
unless you tell her.

03:37.251 --> 03:40.652
Well, can't I just ignore
the other kids more?

03:40.654 --> 03:43.021
You are going to have
a daddy-daughter day
with Erica,

03:43.023 --> 03:45.357
like you used to do
when she was little.

03:45.359 --> 03:46.725
A whole day?

03:46.727 --> 03:49.728
