like spending a day
with myself.

03:49.730 --> 03:50.963
It's why I nap.

03:50.965 --> 03:51.697
You're doing it, Murray,

03:51.699 --> 03:53.832
and you're gonna smile
and have fun, damn it.

03:53.834 --> 03:57.002
Fine. I'll do
your daddy-daughter thing.

03:57.004 --> 03:59.605
But just know
you're overreacting.

03:59.607 --> 04:02.641
I'm quite comfortable
with the girl.

04:04.244 --> 04:06.645
Thanks, Mom.
Mmm-hmm.

04:06.713 --> 04:08.347
