<i>♪ I'm twisted up inside</i>

04:14.054 --> 04:18.657
<i>♪ But nonetheless</i>
<i>I feel the need to say</i>

04:20.493 --> 04:21.426
<i>♪ I don't know the future</i>

04:21.428 --> 04:25.731
<i>♪ But the past keeps getting</i>
<i>clearer every day ♪</i>

04:25.733 --> 04:27.132
<i>It was September 8th,</i>
<i>1980-something.</i>

04:27.134 --> 04:32.337
<i>School hadn't started yet,</i>
<i>but any chance of</i>
<i>me being cool was gone.</i>

04:32.339 --> 04:33.005
Knock knock, kiddo.

04:33.007 --> 04:36.708
ADAM: I'm not comin' out.
Mom took me school shopping.

04:36.710 --> 04:38.844
