04:52.159 --> 04:53.558
I don't even like trains.

04:53.560 --> 04:54.893
The sweater says you do.

04:54.895 --> 04:56.428
Well, the sweater's a lie!

04:56.430 --> 04:57.162
Okay, calm down.

04:57.164 --> 04:59.531
