It comes with a hat!

05:04.505 --> 05:08.540
Okay. We gotta
hit the mall, and fast.

05:08.542 --> 05:09.675
You'll take me shopping?

05:09.677 --> 05:12.978
Absolutely.
Okay, off we go.

05:12.980 --> 05:15.614
