(CHUCKLES)

05:27.660 --> 05:31.330
(LOWERED VOICE)
I'll handle her later.

05:31.332 --> 05:33.432
<i>While Pops was saving me</i>
<i>from the tradition</i>
<i>with my mom,</i>

05:33.434 --> 05:39.271
