I'm really not hungry.

05:48.981 --> 05:50.482
Nachos.

05:50.484 --> 05:52.484
Am I here as
some kind of punishment?

05:52.486 --> 05:55.220
No! No, no, no.
We're havin' fun.

05:55.222 --> 05:59.491
Hangin'. Talkin'.
Makin' memories.

06:02.528 --> 06:03.028
Okay.

06:03.030 --> 06:05.263
<i>But after an hour,</i>
<i>the only memory they made</i>

06:05.265 --> 06:07.632
<i>was my dad getting rough</i>
<i>with the claw machine.</i>

06:07.634 --> 06:10.535
Come on. Come to p...
What?

06:10.537 --> 06:11.737
(MACHINE BEEPING)

06:11.739 --> 06:12.704
That unicorn is rigged.

06:12.706 --> 06:13.638
