plenty dangerous.

07:07.194 --> 07:09.428
Do you remember
Marge Grossman's son Trace?

07:09.430 --> 07:11.797
(SCOFFS)
He got his foot stuck
in the track.

07:11.799 --> 07:12.664
Train came by,
cut it right off.

07:12.666 --> 07:16.134
If you could get me
a sweater of that,
then I'd wear it.

07:16.136 --> 07:20.906
Come on, Bev.
Let's not make a thing
out of this, okay?

07:25.445 --> 07:26.077
Okay.

07:26.079 --> 07:30.415
