07:38.892 --> 07:41.526
See, kid? I told ya
she'd come around.

07:41.528 --> 07:42.027
(CHUCKLES)

07:42.029 --> 07:44.196
<i>But Beverly Goldberg</i>
<i>does not come around.</i>

07:44.198 --> 07:46.298
<i>I was so blinded</i>
<i>by the bright neon,</i>

07:46.300 --> 07:49.835
