08:18.131 --> 08:20.966
Okay, uh, don't take this
the wrong way,

08:20.968 --> 08:22.601
but no one
with a hint of cool

08:22.603 --> 08:26.404
would ever set foot on...
Oh, my God!

08:26.406 --> 08:28.840
