08:29.575 --> 08:33.011
<i>That's right,</i>
<i>they'd stumbled upon</i>
<i>Barry's secret world...</i>

08:33.013 --> 08:36.014
<i>A world he wanted no one</i>
<i>to know about.</i>

08:38.417 --> 08:39.484
