<i>♪ Come sail away with me</i>

19:51.524 --> 19:54.992
<i>♪ Come sail away,</i>
<i>come sail away</i>

19:54.994 --> 19:58.095
<i>♪ Come sail away</i>
<i>with me, baby</i>

19:58.097 --> 20:01.832
<i>♪ Come sail away,</i>
<i>come sail away</i>

20:01.834 --> 20:04.569
<i>♪ Come sail away with me</i>

20:04.571 --> 20:07.905
<i>♪ Come sail away,</i>
<i>come sail away</i>

20:07.907 --> 20:11.742
<i>♪ Come sail away with me</i>

20:12.077 --> 20:14.612
Look how much fun
Mommy's having.

20:14.614 --> 20:16.113
Hi!

20:20.352 --> 20:23.955
(MUSIC PLAYING)
It's a work in progress,
but here it goes.

