<i>♪ My name is Barry,</i>
<i>but they call me Big Tasty</i>

20:32.165 --> 20:35.533
<i>♪ I'm the number one rapper</i>
<i>in the U.S.-asty</i>

20:35.535 --> 20:38.536
<i>♪ My rhymes are fresh,</i>
<i>my flow is hasty</i>

20:38.538 --> 20:41.505
<i>♪ You'll be eatin' up my words</i>
