20:45.645 --> 20:47.478
<i>♪ Big</i>

20:47.613 --> 20:48.546
What's happening?

20:48.548 --> 20:52.016
I'll tell you
what's happening.
He's a moron.

20:52.018 --> 20:54.151
My God, stop it.

20:56.688 --> 20:57.555
<i>Stop it. Stop it.</i>

20:57.557 --> 21:00.591
<i>I am watching,</i>
<i>and it's aggravating!</i>

21:00.593 --> 21:01.826
ADAM:  <i>Is it annoying?</i>

21:01.828 --> 21:02.460
<i>Where you going?</i>

21:02.462 --> 21:04.929
<i>I can't help you!</i>
<i>I don't know</i>
<i>what to do about it!</i>

21:04.931 --> 21:06.697
<i>You have a family here!</i>

21:06.699 --> 21:07.298
BEVERLY:  <i>Murray!</i>

21:07.300 --> 21:08.766
